  m_Name: Loki_JH
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ISUGameDev.SpearGame.Dialogue.Dialogue
  dialogueStrings:
  - "Valkyrie\u2026"
  - I knew you would travel far to reach me, but those travels have now come to an
    end.
  - "In all honesty, I\u2019m surprised you have not grown tired of me. But that
    is not the point of this."
  - Ragnarok is inevitable.
  - "It is written\u2026destined to happen."
  - And now it is time for Surtr to return to the 9 realms.
  - '[v]Not today, Loki.'
  - '[v]Stand down now or perish.'
  - Hahaha!
  - You are so full of hope.
  - "\u2018Stand down or perish.\u2019 Hahaha!"
  - "\u2026"
  - '[d]No.'
